@startuml provider_sequence
title Provider Flow
hide footbox

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor          #555555
    ActorBorderColor    #555555
    LifeLineBorderColor #999999
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #EEEEEE
    ParticipantBorderColor #555555
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #B3D9FF
    NoteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
    NoteBorderColor     #999999
}

actor "Provider Application\n(EU.EORI.NLPLEGMA)" as Provider
participant "Kong API Gateway\n(kong-standalone:8000)" as Kong
participant "iSHARE Satellite\n(ishare-satellite:8080)" as Satellite
participant "Orion-LD\n(fiware-orion-ld:1026)" as Orion

== Step 1: Provider creates self-signed iSHARE JWT ==

Provider -> Provider : gen_token.py:\nbuild JWT with\n• iss=EU.EORI.NLPLEGMA\n• sub=EU.EORI.NLPLEGMA\n• aud=EU.EORI.NLPLEGMA\n• x5c=[client.pem, ca.pem]\nsign with client.key (RS256)

note right of Provider
The Provider is the local authority.
It signs its own JWT with the provider
certificate. No login required.
end note

== Step 2: Provider sends request to Kong ==

Provider -> Kong : GET /ngsi-ld/v1/entities?type=HouseholdMeasurement\nAuthorization: Bearer <iSHARE JWT>

activate Kong

== Step 3: Kong validates the JWT ==

Kong -> Kong : ngsi-ishare-policies plugin:\nparse JWT, extract x5c chain

Kong -> Satellite : GET /token\n(Kong authenticates as EU.EORI.NLPLEGMA)
activate Satellite
Satellite --> Kong : access_token
deactivate Satellite

Kong -> Satellite : GET /trusted_list\nAuthorization: Bearer <access_token>
activate Satellite
Satellite --> Kong : List of trusted CA fingerprints\n(includes Plegma CA)
deactivate Satellite

Kong -> Kong : Verify JWT signature against\nx5c chain & trusted CA list:\nVALID ✓

== Step 4: Kong checks issuer ==

Kong -> Kong : iss (EU.EORI.NLPLEGMA) ==\nlocal authority (EU.EORI.NLPLEGMA)?\nYES → no delegation needed\n(Provider has full access)

== Step 5: Kong forwards request to Orion-LD ==

Kong -> Orion : GET /ngsi-ld/v1/entities?type=HouseholdMeasurement
activate Orion
Orion --> Kong : 200 OK\n[HouseholdMeasurement entities]
deactivate Orion

Kong --> Provider : 200 OK\n[HouseholdMeasurement entities]
deactivate Kong

@enduml
